{"type":"message","id":"26dab6e7","parentId":"f1d8bef3","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:38:44.700Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_br2o2ynjxgbl_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5284\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3097\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 023814 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. The pulse logs are available and I need to implement the classifier to measure invariant/variant patterns.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"nimble-daisy","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5284\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3097\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 023814 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. The pulse logs are available and I need to implement the classifier to measure invariant/variant patterns.\n","name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774334324698}}
